title: 47 in. Garden Spade Shovel
description: This all-steel garden spade features a D-handle design for comfortable, two-handed control whether you re digging over a vegetable border, creating a trench or slicing through turf. A sharpened blade cuts into hard ground with ease, and an oversized step provides a comfortable platform for your foot to provide even more power. The welded steel construction makes this garden spade virtually unbreakable, and a powder coat prevents rust and makes it easy to keep your spade clean. Lifetime warranty.
